name: Circumstances, Questions, and Routinities
description:
Capturing mundanity, same objects again and again, each emulsion represent growing and shifting of how we perceived things.
-
It’s difficult to remained truthful to yourself,
It’s even more difficult not to asking yourself,
What is what and which is which,
After all, you choose what you want,
Based on several things that followed.
.
Everything is nothing in the end.
